{"tid":1470413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非及律師請進】申請禁制令禁止使用催淚彈可行性","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:39:54.000Z","uid":8839,"like":109,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"1afd5a64b960d06d4e3d9d6430eb7eb61ba093a0","tid":1470413,"uid":8839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:16:48.000Z","msg":"都係借朋友AC<br />\n<br />\n既然機場申請禁制令，我地都可以以其人之道，還治其人之身，唔比狗用催淚彈。<br />\n狗亂咁用亂咁射催淚彈既片大把，而且影響到普通市民，仲要係過期既，再加上國際組織都有出聲話佢地唔合乎使用標準。<br />\n<br />\n如果法庭唔批，證明平亂&gt;普通市民生命安全；<br />\n如果法庭批，佢地少左樣武器用；<br />\n如果法庭批而照放，文宣可以大大力攻佢地藐視法庭；<br />\n如果法庭批而照放，而法庭之後咩都做唔到，咁就法治已死。<br />\n<br />\n唔好處係燒錢都未必成功。<br />\n<br />\n求討論甚至有人實行。"},{"pid":"4c3af9665b242d2f2f520ad30af749ae8e10fa62","tid":1470413,"uid":142854,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:22:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇用架啦 要勇武對待<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割席<br />\n兄弟上山<br />\n香港加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"baec0b29c334e6c1ea3c422e1465c80de5bcf69b","tid":1470413,"uid":61503,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"4c3af9665b242d2f2f520ad30af749ae8e10fa62","tid":1470413,"uid":142854,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:22:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇用架啦 要勇武對待<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割席<br />\n兄弟上山<br />\n香港加油</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"勇武唔係問題，但問題係手足拉下又一個，敵軍無損失人手呢個係一個問題"},{"pid":"a74d4762d77a2777d07516620c4fe1a14daf08a2","tid":1470413,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c48745ab931a9289502c26efa84d5eff819403d","tid":1470413,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"baec0b29c334e6c1ea3c422e1465c80de5bcf69b","tid":1470413,"uid":61503,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"4c3af9665b242d2f2